  "pinData": {},
  "meta": { "description": "Native n8n AI Agent: chat with a VYREX SOC analyst backed by a self-hosted Ollama model. The agent calls VYREX endpoints as TOOLS (get_ranking, explain_finding, investigate_incident, dispatch_alerts) to answer with real evidence. One-time setup: create an 'Ollama' credential in n8n (Base URL http://ollama:11434) named 'VYREX Ollama'. Open the workflow and use the built-in Chat. Containment stays behind two-person approval. See docs/AI-ANALYST.md." }
